  "detailed_description": "<h1>Wishlist an upcoming card battler!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Moonstone Island</strong> is a creature-collecting life-sim set in an open world with 100 islands to explore. Make friends, brew potions, collect Spirits, and test your strength in card-based encounters to complete your Alchemy training! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/b10d203b7d12a24d46f0cc4204ef4feb.poster.avif?t=1771272713\" width=620 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/b10d203b7d12a24d46f0cc4204ef4feb.webm?t=1771272713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Spend time on islands in the sky!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Following your village's tradition, you must move to an island in the sky to complete your Alchemy training. Armed with a team of nature spirits, magical potions, and the support of your new friends, you'll explore ancient temples, dangerous dungeons, and hostile biomes to uncover the dark secret of Moonstone Island. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/9d39ee259e0a2df0ed82b1d2a5b7a76b.poster.avif?t=1771272713\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/9d39ee259e0a2df0ed82b1d2a5b7a76b.webm?t=1771272713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Befriend NPCs, become a member of the community, go on dates, fall in love, and marry the villager of your dreams!  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Build a new home on any of the 100 islands in your procedurally generated world </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Grow crops and flowers to brew potions and tame spirits. Cultivate ingredients to cook your fave dishes for fun and stat bonuses! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Customize and decorate your home to make it uniquely yours with over 300 decorations </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/478718d40c724dc5ed678084df9ce227.poster.avif?t=1771272713\" width=620 height=104 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/478718d40c724dc5ed678084df9ce227.webm?t=1771272713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Travel by balloon, broom, and glider through unique biomes to reach the outer edges of the world to uncover the secrets of your floating home in the sky</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Tame and befriend wild spirits to fight alongside you - Over 70 Spirits to tame!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Discover and explore dungeons to earn upgrades, collect loot and uncover secrets - Or take on the INFINIDUNGEON for neverending battles and rewards!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Optimize your character with unique skills and upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Craft dozens of items and vehicles to prepare for the treacherous wilderness</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/a15839182fff8f7be76279a8e17b284f.poster.avif?t=1771272713\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/a15839182fff8f7be76279a8e17b284f.webm?t=1771272713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/a15839182fff8f7be76279a8e17b284f.mp4?t=1771272713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Since we launched on September 20, 2023 we’ve been working hard to add more functionality and fun to the game, including:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cooking!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >41 new cards!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 50 new and free decorative items!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Marriage!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Infinidungeon!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character Customization – Dress your alchemist up in adorable fits to reflect your play!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More QoL improvements than we can count!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/0ed76c682507f4f986246f7a55a961ce.poster.avif?t=1771272713\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/0ed76c682507f4f986246f7a55a961ce.webm?t=1771272713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/0ed76c682507f4f986246f7a55a961ce.mp4?t=1771272713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/56e1f2aa026b0e1a1a0ff2987d8a0d48.avif?t=1771272713\" width=600 height=123 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Moonstone Island</strong> is a creature-collecting life-sim set in an open world with 100 islands to explore. Make friends, brew potions, collect Spirits, and test your strength in card-based encounters to complete your Alchemy training! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/b10d203b7d12a24d46f0cc4204ef4feb.poster.avif?t=1771272713\" width=620 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/b10d203b7d12a24d46f0cc4204ef4feb.webm?t=1771272713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Spend time on islands in the sky!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Following your village's tradition, you must move to an island in the sky to complete your Alchemy training. Armed with a team of nature spirits, magical potions, and the support of your new friends, you'll explore ancient temples, dangerous dungeons, and hostile biomes to uncover the dark secret of Moonstone Island. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/9d39ee259e0a2df0ed82b1d2a5b7a76b.poster.avif?t=1771272713\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/9d39ee259e0a2df0ed82b1d2a5b7a76b.webm?t=1771272713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Befriend NPCs, become a member of the community, go on dates, fall in love, and marry the villager of your dreams!  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Build a new home on any of the 100 islands in your procedurally generated world </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Grow crops and flowers to brew potions and tame spirits. Cultivate ingredients to cook your fave dishes for fun and stat bonuses! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Customize and decorate your home to make it uniquely yours with over 300 decorations </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/478718d40c724dc5ed678084df9ce227.poster.avif?t=1771272713\" width=620 height=104 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/478718d40c724dc5ed678084df9ce227.webm?t=1771272713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Travel by balloon, broom, and glider through unique biomes to reach the outer edges of the world to uncover the secrets of your floating home in the sky</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Tame and befriend wild spirits to fight alongside you - Over 70 Spirits to tame!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Discover and explore dungeons to earn upgrades, collect loot and uncover secrets - Or take on the INFINIDUNGEON for neverending battles and rewards!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Optimize your character with unique skills and upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Craft dozens of items and vehicles to prepare for the treacherous wilderness</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/a15839182fff8f7be76279a8e17b284f.poster.avif?t=1771272713\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/a15839182fff8f7be76279a8e17b284f.webm?t=1771272713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/a15839182fff8f7be76279a8e17b284f.mp4?t=1771272713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Since we launched on September 20, 2023 we’ve been working hard to add more functionality and fun to the game, including:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cooking!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >41 new cards!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 50 new and free decorative items!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Marriage!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Infinidungeon!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character Customization – Dress your alchemist up in adorable fits to reflect your play!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More QoL improvements than we can count!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/0ed76c682507f4f986246f7a55a961ce.poster.avif?t=1771272713\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/0ed76c682507f4f986246f7a55a961ce.webm?t=1771272713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658150/extras/0ed76c682507f4f986246f7a55a961ce.mp4?t=1771272713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared